songs.title: There’s a Heaven
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
There's a Heaven for us
And there's a Heaven for me, yeah
There's a Heaven for us
Good Lord let me be, yeah
Good Lord let me see

[Verse]
Maybe I need new eyes
Maybe I don't need one at all
Welcome to your brand new life
You lost everything just to gain it all

[Chorus]
There's a Heaven for us
I know there's a Heaven for me, yeah
And there's a Heaven for us, yeah
Good Lord let me be, yeah
Good Lord let me see

[Outro]
There's a Heaven for us
There's a Heaven for me
There's a Heaven for us
Good Lord let me be
